description: The SPDR NYSE Technology ETF seeks to provide investment results that, before fees and expenses, correspond generally to the total return performance of the NYSE Technology Index (the “Index”).The NYSE Technology Index is composed of 35 leading US-listed technology-related companies. The Index is equal-weighted at its annual rebalance. The index comprises stocks in the Information Technology sector and technology-related stocks in the Consumer Discretionary sector.
name: SPDR NYSE Technology ETF
